member.summary:
Type of action to broadcast. Choose one, depending on what the user is about to receive:
 for text messages,
 for photos,
 or  for
videos,  or
 for voice notes,
 for general files,
 for location data,
 or  for
video notes

Use this method to send video files, Telegram clients support mp4 videos (other formats may be sent as
). Bots can currently send video files of up to 50 MB in size, this limit may be
changed in the future.

member.param:
Type of action to broadcast. Choose one, depending on what the user is about to receive:
 for text messages,
 for photos,
 or  for
videos,  or
 for voice notes,
 for general files,
 for location data,
 or  for
video notes

member.summary:
Optional. Use this parameter if you want to show the keyboard to specific users only. Targets:
users that are @mentioned in the of the object;
if the bot's message is a reply (has ), sender of the original message.
